  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Chop onions and mince garlic. Slice carrots and zucchini into thin rounds. Chop green or red bell peppers.",
    "Combine sherry, olive oil, soy sauce, pepper flakes, red pepper flakes, and garlic powder in a small bowl. Mix well.",
    "In a large mixing bowl, combine the roasted vegetables with the marinade mixture, tossing until all vegetables are coated evenly.",
    "Transfer to a baking dish. Sprinkle sesame seeds on top if using.",
    "Roast for 20-25 minutes or until the vegetables are tender and lightly browned.",
    "Serve hot as a side dish or over rice."
